headline: Brandy Zadrozny moves from NBC News to MSNBC as the network’s post-Comcast newsroom takes shape
summary: The Emmy-winning journalist is known for her coverage of the internet and disinformation. MSNBC and NBC News are in the process of decoupling.

headline: Paramount Settles Trump’s ‘60 Minutes’ Suit for $16 Million
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Paramount Global reached a settlement with President Donald Trump over a lawsuit that alleged election interference by the company’s CBS news network when it showed two different versions of a 60 Minutes interview with then-Vice President Kamala Harris in October.
